    "overview": "Commercial outdoor benches for parks, schools, campuses, plazas, resorts, and public gathering spaces—built for heavy use and long service life. Materials include recycled plastic, wood, powder-coated steel, thermoplastic coating, aluminum, and thermally modified ash, with low-maintenance options for harsh outdoor climates. Choose backed or backless designs in multiple lengths and colors, with portable, wall-mounted, surface-mount, or inground installation."
